No. Why?
If you never met him,

26:43.870 --> 26:45.599
how'd you know
he had children?

26:48.100 --> 26:50.489
I-I didn't. I...
Stop.

26:50.540 --> 26:51.837
The only thing
worse than a lie

26:51.870 --> 26:53.360
