I did know Walcott
from the circus days.

27:11.760 --> 27:13.921
He knew
I could move things,
so when...

27:13.960 --> 27:17.521
When he decided
to move drugs,
he gave me a call.

27:17.560 --> 27:19.061
I-I didn't know What was
gonna happen to you,

27:19.100 --> 27:22.399
so, you know, I-I...
(SIGHS)

27:25.140 --> 27:27.904
I did what they did,
and... And I freelanced.

27:30.080 --> 27:33.277
Androssani was just
trying to make his rate.

27:33.310 --> 27:36.814
I don't condone it,
hence the 15% surcharge.

27:36.850 --> 27:38.488
Walcott came up
With the idea

27:38.520 --> 27:41.648
to use my infrastructure
to move drugs.

27:41.690 --> 27:46.081
Which was bad enough,
but What you did
was considerably worse.

27:46.130 --> 27:48.496
You made his idea happen.

27:48.530 --> 27:51.328
You were the logistical
mastermind.

27:51.370 --> 27:56.660
Without you, his idea
was just that... An idea.

27:56.700 --> 27:59.931
Thanks to you,
it's now a reality.

27:59.970 --> 28:01.938
Red...
I know about
the network, Smokey.

28:01.980 --> 28:04.005
The shipments of meth
you're making

28:04.050 --> 28:07.099
to Phoenix, Miami,
Seattle, Boston,

28:07.150 --> 28:09.118
and everywhere
along the way.

28:09.150 --> 28:11.141
I didn't turn you in
to the cops,
if that's What you think.

28:11.190 --> 28:14.956
What I think is
that you're a born carny.

28:14.990 --> 28:18.482
You're a con man._
You're Simply hard-Wired

