from us?

30:50.610 --> 30:52.407
ARAM: Because she was never
in the diner parking lot.

30:52.450 --> 30:55.317
I pulled security footage
from the trucking company
across the street.

30:55.350 --> 30:57.773
Check out the Buick
With the "Bush/Quayle"
bumper sticker.

30:57.820 --> 30:59.811
So she made a getaway
doing the speed limit.

30:59.850 --> 31:05.322
The car is registered
to an Agathe Tyche,
66, of Camden, Delaware.

31:05.360 --> 31:08.750
And she has
a very, very sad story.

31:08.800 --> 31:11.826
Miss Tyche was an upstanding
citizen of her community,

31:11.870 --> 31:14.634
married to
a lifelong gambler,
Lou Tyche.

31:14.670 --> 31:19.039
In 1986, Lou bought a lottery
ticket and won $87 million,

31:19.070 --> 31:20.901
largest jackpot
in Delaware history.

31:20.940 --> 31:22.373
Made national news.

31:22.410 --> 31:24.002
I remember this story.
There was a child.

31:24.050 --> 31:27.201
Second child being born.
It was a long, intense labor.

31:27.250 --> 31:29.377
Lou waited in the hospital,
but at one point,

31:29.420 --> 31:32.048
he left With her son to make
a run to a convenience store

31:32.090 --> 31:33.341
and bought
a lottery ticket.

31:33.390 --> 31:35.210
COOPER: There was an accident.
The son died.

31:35.260 --> 31:36.557
The father
was badly injured.

31:36.590 --> 31:38.558
ARAM: And _the ticket
was a Winner.

31:38.590 --> 31:41.457
At the same time
that Agathe was giving
birth to her daughter,

31:41.500 --> 31:43.525
her son was dying
three floors away

31:43.560 --> 31:45.323
While her husband
was in surgery.

31:45.370 --> 31:47.122
The ticket was returned
to her by a medic

31:47.170 --> 31:49.536
Who found it
in her husband's effects.

31:49.570 --> 31:51.458
Looks like we've found
Lady Luck.

31:51.510 --> 31:53.808
Looks like you're
going to Delaware.

31:53.840 --> 31:56.172
(KNOCK ON DOOR, DOOR OPENS)

31:56.210 --> 31:58.508
Agathe Tyche?

31:58.550 --> 32:00.643
What? Uh, no,
that's my mother.

32:00.680 --> 32:03.012
Agents Keen and Ressler, FBI.
Is she here?

32:03.050 --> 32:05.143
No.
Do you know
Where she is?

32:05.190 --> 32:06.487
I don't.

32:06.520 --> 32:09.489
What can you tell us about the
lottery that your parents won?

32:09.520 --> 32:12.853
Lottery? What does that
have to do With anything?

32:12.890 --> 32:15.358
Well, we understand your
father won $87 million.

32:15.400 --> 32:18.722
Yeah. Decades ago. My mom
gave all that money away.

32:18.770 --> 32:19.964
Why would she do that?

32:22.570 --> 32:24.868
Because the day he won

32:24.910 --> 32:26.605
was the day that
he got in a car accident

32:26.640 --> 32:28.904
that killed my brother
and paralyzed my father.

32:30.910 --> 32:32.377
He died a few months after.

32:33.580 --> 32:35.343
She connected the money
With their deaths

32:35.380 --> 32:36.870
and didn't want anything
to do With it.

32:36.920 --> 32:39.582
That may be
What she told you,
but the truth is,

32:39.620 --> 32:41.781
she kept the winnings
and has been using them
for years.

32:41.820 --> 32:45.722
She's using it
as a slush fund to ï¬nance
a series of murders.

32:45.760 --> 32:48.456
(TELEVISION PLAYING)

32:50.330 --> 32:52.662
She told my son
she may never see him again,

32:52.700 --> 32:54.099
and I couldn't understand...

32:54.140 --> 32:56.267
LIZ: Because she knew
we were coming.

32:56.300 --> 32:58.700
Ma'am, if you have any idea
Where your mother might be,

32:58.740 --> 33:00.059
you need to tell us.

33:00.110 --> 33:01.702
LIZ: (OVER PHONE) She's gone,

33:01.740 --> 33:03.401
and her daughter says
she doesn't know where.

33:03.440 --> 33:04.907
You believe her?
RESSLER: We do.

33:04.950 --> 33:06.577
She lied to everyone,
including her.

33:06.610 --> 33:08.373
Apparently, she told
her daughter that she gave

33:08.420 --> 33:10.638
the lottery money away
after her husband died.

33:10.680 --> 33:12.341
Wait. After?

33:12.390 --> 33:14.881
Her husband died less than
a year after his accident.

33:14.920 --> 33:16.478
No. No, no, no, no.
That's not right.

33:16.520 --> 33:19.125
I pulled a death certificate
for the son,

33:19.160 --> 33:20.821
but there was nothing
for the husband.

33:20.860 --> 33:23.124
In fact, the Delaware State
Gaming Commission

33:23.160 --> 33:24.661
is still recording
annuity checks

33:24.700 --> 33:25.997
sent to an address
near Wilmington.

33:26.030 --> 33:29.295
Aram, send us that address
and get us HRT
out of Quantico.

33:29.340 --> 33:30.830
MAN ON TV:
Jumper! Jumper!

33:30.870 --> 33:33.065
Bad news, Lou.
The police are onto us.

33:33.110 --> 33:35.476
I pray they don't drag
Moira into this.

33:35.510 --> 33:38.104
Lord knows
we didn't want that
for our baby girl,

33:38.150 --> 33:41.574
the one bright spot
in our lives.

33:41.620 --> 33:42.746
(SIRENS WAILING)

33:42.780 --> 33:44.919
If there's no
death certificate...

33:44.950 --> 33:46.781
Then the father's
still alive.

33:46.820 --> 33:49.914
But Why would she lie,
to her daughter,
of all people?

33:49.960 --> 33:52.428
(LAUGHS)
Okay. I get it.

33:52.460 --> 33:54.826
You can't always
trust family.

33:54.860 --> 33:57.658
But that could mean...

33:57.700 --> 33:59.292
The father's in on it.

34:01.470 --> 34:03.563
**

34:05.170 --> 34:09.129
We had a good run.
Didn't we?

34:09.180 --> 34:11.501
Wasn't all a waste.

34:11.550 --> 34:13.609
(IRON LUNG CLICKING)

34:13.650 --> 34:15.345
I guess this is goodbye.

34:15.380 --> 34:18.838
I can't exactly take you
With me, now, can I?

34:18.890 --> 34:22.656
I had plans for
the rest of the money,
more families to save.

34:22.690 --> 34:23.952
(SIRENS WAILING)

34:23.990 --> 34:25.855
At least
I have the satisfaction

34:25.890 --> 34:27.721
of knowing some
of this blood money

34:27.760 --> 34:29.694
protected others
from our hell.

34:29.730 --> 34:31.368
(SIRENS APPROACHING)

34:32.100 --> 34:33.692
We did good, Lou.

34:36.500 --> 34:37.899
LI_Z: FBI!
Move! Sit down, lady.

34:37.940 --> 34:39.407
RESSLER:
Put the gun down.

34:39.440 --> 34:41.169
It's over, Agathe.
Oh, I know.

34:41.210 --> 34:42.632
I need you
to put that gun down.

34:42.680 --> 34:44.238
We don't want anyone
to get hurt now.

34:44.280 --> 34:47.499
Hurt? You can't hurt me.
I died years ago.

34:47.550 --> 34:51.077
My life was
gambled away cheap.
My firstborn gone.

34:51.120 --> 34:53.714
I swore then, I'd do
everything in my power

34:53.750 --> 34:55.809
to keep people safe
from that kind of destruction.

34:55.860 --> 34:57.179
RESSLER:
Put that gun down.

34:57.220 --> 34:59.450
And God answered
my prayers.

34:59.490 --> 35:04.393
I used those cursed Winnings
to help other
suffering families.

35:04.430 --> 35:06.091
A perfect system

35:06.130 --> 35:07.722
to guarantee
they'd never be ruined

35:07.770 --> 35:09.863
like I was, like we were.

35:09.900 --> 35:11.367
You need to
put that gun down.

35:11.410 --> 35:14.436
Gamblers. They're the
worst kind of addicts.

35:14.480 --> 35:15.879
They think
they deserve to win

35:15.910 --> 35:17.832
While everyone
around them loses.

35:17.880 --> 35:19.541
**

35:21.480 --> 35:22.469
Not this time.

35:23.320 --> 35:25.538
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

35:25.590 --> 35:28.286
(GASPING)

35:28.320 --> 35:29.617
She tripped the breaker.

35:29.660 --> 35:30.888
I don't know where it is.
Find it!

35:30.920 --> 35:32.251
(ALARM BEEPING)

35:32.290 --> 35:35.521
(WHIMPERS)
Get him out of there!

35:35.560 --> 35:36.629
(ALARM BEEPING)

35:36.660 --> 35:37.922
Got to find
that breaker!

35:37.960 --> 35:39.689
(HANDCUFFS CLICKING)

35:39.730 --> 35:41.436
Speak up, Lou!

35:41.470 --> 35:43.290
(GASPING)

35:43.340 --> 35:46.059
Last chance to atone
for your Sin.

35:46.110 --> 35:48.101
(WHIMPERING)

35:55.450 --> 35:56.474
Are you saying

35:56.520 --> 35:58.613
