after the car accident?

35:58.650 --> 35:59.878
No, he was paralyzed.

35:59.920 --> 36:02.252
That he's been alive
all these years?

36:02.290 --> 36:05.453
Your mother kept him
on a mechanical respirator.

36:05.490 --> 36:07.321
In hiding. From me?

36:07.360 --> 36:10.090
I can't imagine how hard
this is to hear,
but all these years,

36:10.130 --> 36:12.325
your mother has kept
your father hostage.

36:12.370 --> 36:14.429
Why would anyone do that?
To punish him.

36:14.470 --> 36:16.836
She believes your
father's addiction
destroyed your family,

36:16.870 --> 36:18.269
so she came up with a way

36:18.310 --> 36:20.301
to prevent other families
from being destroyed.

36:20.340 --> 36:24.071
By killing addicts, people
Who can't help themselves.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.771
It's because they
couldn't help themselves

36:25.810 --> 36:27.778
that she thought
they had to die.

36:27.810 --> 36:31.246
And when they did,
their family's fortunes
were restored.

36:31.290 --> 36:32.939
Your mother's a troubled woman
Who's gonna spend

36:32.990 --> 36:34.958
the rest of her life
in prison.

36:34.990 --> 36:37.811
There's no con_solation
for this, for losmg her.

36:37.860 --> 36:39.680
But you do have
your father back,

36:39.730 --> 36:42.426
as well_ as what's left
of his Winnings.

36:42.460 --> 36:45.190
I hope that affords you
some solace.

36:45.800 --> 36:47.028
Can I talk to her?

36:50.200 --> 36:52.464
What?
I think you know.

36:54.310 --> 36:56.232
An example
had to be made.

36:56.280 --> 36:58.009
(DOOR OPENS)

36:58.040 --> 36:59.701
Hey! (LAUGHS)
You came!

36:59.750 --> 37:02.173
Of course!
We wouldn't miss it!

37:02.220 --> 37:04.040
Ahh.
Look at you, Janet.

37:04.080 --> 37:06.685
Ohh. Hi. Hi.
It's good to see you.

37:06.720 --> 37:08.756
JAN ET: Yes.

37:08.790 --> 37:11.827
I can't thank you enough
for everything you've done.

37:11.860 --> 37:14.556
I've never been thanked
for emeg someone before.

37:14.600 --> 37:18.229
You didn't just give me
a new house. _
You gave me a new life.

37:18.270 --> 37:19.669
It's the least I could do

37:19.700 --> 37:22.237
for keeping my relationship
With the task force secret.

37:22.270 --> 37:24.329
Oh, but you've done
so much more than that.

37:24.370 --> 37:26.702
Your contributions.
There... There'd be

37:26.740 --> 37:29.379
no arts program here
at Shermer Without them.

37:29.410 --> 37:31.901
What you're going to
hear tonight,

37:31.950 --> 37:34.202
none of it would've
happened Without you.

37:34.250 --> 37:35.911
Thank you, Janet.

37:35.950 --> 37:37.872
You're the best,
Mr. Reddington.

37:37.920 --> 37:40.787
Imagine that!
(BOTH LAUGH)

