The story goes that
after she killed herself,

38:02.140 --> 38:03.869
Rostova's parents
went into hiding.

38:03.910 --> 38:05.343
Father was KGB,

38:05.380 --> 38:07.200
so people assumed he helped
the mother disappear.

38:07.250 --> 38:09.775
But if,
and this is a big if,

38:09.820 --> 38:11.117
if Rostova didn't die,

38:11.150 --> 38:13.243
if she knew people
were coming for her...

38:13.290 --> 38:15.554
She'd be the one
to protect her parents.

38:16.790 --> 38:18.326
81 and 59.

38:18.360 --> 38:21.591
The passenger
was 22 years older
than Rostova.

38:21.630 --> 38:23.052
Do you have a D.O.B.
on the mother?

38:23.100 --> 38:26.228
We do. She was 22
When Katarina was born.

38:26.270 --> 38:27.521
We didn't find Katarina,

38:27.570 --> 38:30.368
but it's possible
we found her mother.

38:30.400 --> 38:32.436
(APPLAUSE)

38:32.470 --> 38:35.177
**

38:35.210 --> 38:39.249
* Every breath you take

38:39.280 --> 38:43.319
* Every move you make

38:43.350 --> 38:45.386
* Every bond you break

38:45.420 --> 38:47.581
* Every step you take

38:47.620 --> 38:49.383
* I'll be watching you

38:49.420 --> 38:51.479
I'm sorry it turned out
this way.

38:51.530 --> 38:52.656
I am, too.

38:52.690 --> 38:54.089
* Every single day

38:54.130 --> 38:56.291
(CRYING) There's so much
I want to tell you.

38:56.330 --> 38:57.820
It's okay, Mom.

38:57.860 --> 39:00.420
I know everything
I need to know.

39:00.470 --> 39:03.268
The lady that got me to
do this, this Lady Luck,

39:03.300 --> 39:05.006
I'll tell you anything
you want to know about her.

39:05.040 --> 39:06.132
That's good, Henry.

39:06.170 --> 39:08.479
But right now, I'm not
interested in Lady Luck.

39:08.510 --> 39:10.478
First, I want you to tell me
everything you know

39:10.510 --> 39:13.343
about a group called
the Third Estate.

39:13.380 --> 39:17.976
* Can't you see
you belong to me?

