Red was right. Henry Morris is
connected to the Third Estate.

39:21.290 --> 39:23.349
He gave them state-of-the-art
surveillance equipment

39:23.390 --> 39:25.779
so they could penetrate
high-end security systems

39:25.830 --> 39:27.752
in private homes.
Did he give you a name?

39:27.790 --> 39:29.599
No, they contracted
through encrypted

39:29.630 --> 39:31.052
Wire transfers
and dead-drops.

39:31.100 --> 39:35.389
But think about it.
The Third Estate is the 99%.

39:35.440 --> 39:37.658
If they're plotting
against America, where else

39:37.700 --> 39:39.861
are they gonna start
than by attacking the 1%?

39:39.910 --> 39:41.639
Yeah, but it's
a pretty big target.

39:41.680 --> 39:44.649
Yeah, well, it's 99% smaller
than it was a few minutes ago.

39:44.680 --> 39:45.840
I'm gonna go tell Cooper.

39:45.880 --> 39:47.905
Keen, hang on a minute.
Uh...

39:47.950 --> 39:51.113
* Every move you make
Every step you take

39:51.150 --> 39:52.378
(SIGHS)

39:52.420 --> 39:54.809
By the way...

39:54.860 --> 39:57.181
I'm sorry
I snapped at you before.

39:59.060 --> 40:01.551
You've been on Reddington's
case longer than any of us,

40:01.600 --> 40:04.319
